title: Daz3D - LY Vega Davin HD
description:
http://www.daz3d.com/ly-vega-davin-hd

Details

Vega Davin is a lovely warrior girl. With warrior makeups, dark shadows and lips... she is painted and ready for the battle. Because eyebrows should match the hair, Davin gives you the ability to change the color of the eyebrows. More options and more flexibility means a more realistic look.

Options include 8 eye colors and 10 lipsticks and makeups. As always, there are 11 presets that include makeup, and lips for an easy all-in-one solution. Buttons for Anatomical Elements and a No Brow face texture option are included, Plus 4 eyebrow overlays. All textures use the Genesis 3 Female UV maps
